'''德莫特·歐萊瑞'''（Sean Dermot Fintan O'Leary, Jr.，{{bd|1973年|9月24日}}）是[[英國|英國]]的一位節目主持人。他是[[獨立電視台|ITV]]的眾多電視節目和[[BBC廣播二台|BBC廣播二台]]廣播節目的主持人。自2007年開始，他是[[英國版X音素|英國版X音素]]的主持人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-x-factor/news/a788461/its-finally-official-dermot-oleary-is-back-as-x-factor-host-to-replace-olly-murs-and-caroline-flack/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-05-11 |archive-date=2020-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110155653/https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/reality-tv/a788461/its-finally-official-dermot-oleary-makes-dramatic-return-to-host-the-x-factor-a-year-after-he-quit/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾是[[基督少年軍|基督少年軍]]的成員<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?list=PLLJQHjmJHb1qTGu9nMgZQ3O44k0yAF-hG&v=0abhIEz_qvE |title=Dermot discusses his dancing - Live Week 5 - The Xtra Factor 2013 |publisher=YouTube |date=11 November 2013 |accessdate=4 July 2014 |archive-date=2016-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502074430/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0abhIEz_qvE&list=PLLJQHjmJHb1qTGu9nMgZQ3O44k0yAF-hG |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
